Recommendation1:
The disclosure required by paragraph 35 shall include the total energy consumption in MWh related to own operations disaggregated by:
(a) total energy consumption from fossil sources;
(b) total energy consumption from nuclear sources;
(c) total energy consumption from renewable sources disaggregated by:
     (ci) fuel consumption for renewable sources including biomass (also comprising industrial and municipal waste of biologic origin), biofuels, biogas, hydrogen from renewable sources, etc.;
     (cii) consumption of purchased or acquired electricity, heat, steam, and cooling from renewable sources; and
     (ciii) consumption of self-generated non-fuel renewable energy.

